conditions.label: Ticket with reservation : can be exchanged or refunded at no cost prior to departure. After departure, ticket exchangeable and refundable subject to a 50% fee.

Without booking: ticket can be exchanged free of charge for a ticket without seat reservation, a lesser discount or an upgrade before its expiry date. For other exchanges and for refunds, a 10% charge will be applied until the expiry date.

E-ticket service available : e-ticket confirmation must be printed, no stamping, usable only for a trip on the train and date indicated. E-ticket exchangeable and refundable without penalty before departure. After departure, e-ticket non-exchangeable and non-refundable.
Exchange and refund free-of-charge up to 30 minutes after departure.
From 30 minutes before the train departs, ticket can be changed up to two times for the same day and the same journey, and is non-refundable once exchanged
